From 5a31f641fe24f1224e8659cf2ce53fd356b4dec1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: yanguahe <yanguahe@amd.com>
Date: Sat, 14 Mar 2026 10:28:57 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] [AMDGPU] Add SIGEMMScheduleOptimize pass and ISA post-process
 hook

- New pass SIGEMMScheduleOptimize for FMHA GEMM loop optimization:
  T1: Hoist V global_loads before first s_barrier
  T2: Convert serial ds_read/MFMA chains to double-buffered
  T3: Interleave V ds_writes into GEMM1 MFMA slots
- Registered in addPreEmitPass before SIInsertWaitcnts
- Add FLYDSL_POSTPROCESS_ISA env hook in ROCDL Target.cpp
  to run external script on serialized ISA before assembly

Made-with: Cursor
